column10: Good morning all - woke up in a great mood today. Hope you all have to. Proud to be #GirlsLikeUs ! Time for a coffee.
@Lavernecox @MauraLaFae Tx Maura. Grateful to be in sisterhood with you two. #girlslikeus are stronger when we lift one another up!
@janetmock Delighted and honored to be on the list. Thanks! :-) #Girlslikeus
@janetmock I know I haven't transitioned yet, and I understand if you say no, but can I join #girlslikeus? :)
@janetmock That doesn't seem to happen much over here. Everyone seems to stay isolated :( #girlslikeus
@NireBryce Shared understanding is key; and connecting w/ one another chips away at damaging effects of isolation. #girlslikeus
@i_masters You're so sweet! Would you like to be added? I don't want to assume anything ;-) #girlslikeus
Picture at Chicago House Luncheon celebrating the Trans Living Program with @Precious_Jewel & @KennethCole #girlslikeus http://t.co/2uPhScuL
This gallery of Marsha P. Johnson made my evening: http://t.co/QAvqp6Yo HT @Edward_Ndopu #girlslikeus
